e tailored to the customer’s specifications, ensuring an entirely bespoke ownership experience. Aston Martin’s Q Division will oversee personalization, allowing buyers to collaborate closely with designers and engineers in crafting every detail—from livery and materials to seating and control interfaces. Though track-focused, the Valkyrie LM is expected to maintain usability in select private environments, such as closed-road events and curated racing experiences.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/images/design_news/2025/06/only-ten-passionate-collectors-will-own-the-road-legal-aston-martin-valkyrie-lm-hypercar/Aston-Martin-Valkyrie-LM-Hypercar-7.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/images/design_news/2025/06/only-ten-passionate-collectors-will-own-the-road-legal-aston-martin-valkyrie-lm-hypercar/Aston-Martin-Valkyrie-LM-Hypercar-7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/2025/06/09/only-ten-passionate-collectors-will-own-the-road-legal-aston-martin-valkyrie-lm-hypercar/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Only Ten Passionate Collectors will own the Road-legal Aston Martin Valkyrie LM Hypercar\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/images/design_news/2025/06/only-ten-passionate-collectors-will-own-the-road-legal-aston-martin-valkyrie-lm-hypercar/Aston-Martin-Valkyrie-LM-Hypercar-7.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/images/design_news/2025/06/only-ten-passionate-collectors-will-own-the-road-legal-aston-martin-valkyrie-lm-hypercar/Aston-Martin-Valkyrie-LM-Hypercar-8.jpg\" data-src=\"https://www.yankodesign.com/images/design_news/2025/06/only-ten-passionate-collectors-will-own-the-road-legal-aston-martin-valkyrie-lm-hypercar/Aston-Martin-Valkyrie-LM-Hypercar-8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1280\" height=\"960\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url